net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.service.base

Class AbstractDataDumper<C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.service.base.AbstractDataDumper<C>

  • public abstract class AbstractDataDumper<C>
extends Object
    Base class for CSV-generating services. Allows more-or-less declarative construction of CSV reports on the data, including basic aggregation.
